</div>


<div class="mb-test-drive-form-wrapper container-md">
	<form>
		<div class="modal-body">
		  <h2>Wo soll die Probefahrt beginnen?</h2>
		  <div class="row">
		  	<div class="col-xs-12">
		  		<div class="form-group">
		  			<label for="mb-car">Modell wählen</label>
		  			<input type="hidden" id="mb-car" class="form-control" />
		  			<span class="mb-form-sublabel-left" >Kraftstoffverbrauch kombiniert* 5,7l/100km, CO2-Emission***, 129g/km, Energieeffizienzklasse***B</span>
		  		</div> 
		  	</div>
		  </div>
		  <div class="row">
		   	<div class="col-xs-12">
		  		<div class="form-group">
		  			<label for="">Haben Sie besondere Wünsche (Motor, Ausstattungslinie, Sonderausstattung)?</label>
		  			<textarea name="mas" id="" rows="10" class="form-control" ></textarea>
		  		</div>
		  	</div>
		  </div>
		  <div class="row">
		    <div class="col-xs-12">
		      <div class="btn-group btn-group-lg" data-toggle="buttons">
		        <label class="btn btn-primary active">
		          <input type="radio" name="delivery-type" id="option-1" value="delivery-address" autocomplete="off" checked> Wunschadresse
		        </label>
		        <label class="btn btn-primary">
		          <input type="radio" name="delivery-type" id="option-2" value="delivery-dealer" autocomplete="off"> Mercedes-Benz Partner
		        </label>
		      </div>
		    </div>
		  </div>
		  <div class="delivery-type delivery-address">
		    <h3>Bitte geben Sie Ihre Wunschadresse im Hamburger Stadtgebiet an. Wir bringen das Fahrzeug zu Ihnen und holen es nach der Probefahrt wieder ab. </h3>
		    <div class="row">
		      <div class="col-xs-12">
		        <div class="row">
		          <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-4">
		            <div class="form-group">
		              <label for="field-1">{{locale "checkout.step.2.form.delivery.street"}} <sup>*</sup></label>
		              <input type="text" class="form-control data-field" id="field-1" name="deliveryStreet">
		              <span class="form-error-message">Enter value</span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		          <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-2">
		            <div class="form-group">
		              <label for="field-2">{{locale "checkout.step.2.form.delivery.house"}} <sup>*</sup></label>
		              <input type="text" class="form-control data-field" id="field-2" name="deliveryHouse">
		              <span class="form-error-message">Enter value</span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		          <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-6">
		            <div class="form-group">
		              <label for="field-3">{{locale "checkout.step.2.form.delivery.additional"}}</label>
		              <input type="text" class="form-control data-field" id="field-3" name="deliveryAdditional">
		            </div>
		          </div>
		        </div>
		      </div>
		    </div>
		    <div class="row">
		      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
		        <div class="row">
		          <div class="col-xs-3">
		            <div class="form-group">
		              <label for="field-4">{{locale "checkout.step.2.form.delivery.index"}} <sup>*</sup></label>
		              <input type="text" class="form-control data-field" id="field-4" name="deliveryIndex">
		              <span class="form-error-message">Enter value</span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		          <div class="col-xs-9">
		            <div class="form-group">
		              <label for="field-5">{{locale "checkout.step.2.form.delivery.city"}} <sup>*</sup></label>
		              <input type="text" class="form-control data-field" id="field-5" name="deliveryCity">
		              <span class="form-error-message">Enter value</span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		        </div>
		      </div>
		      <label class="mb-form-sublabel"><sup>*</sup> {{locale "checkout.step.2.form.required"}}</label>
		    </div>
		  </div>
		  <div class="delivery-type delivery-dealer hide">
		    <h3>{{locale "checkout.step.2.form.dealer.subtitle"}}</h3>
		    <div class="row">
		      <div class="col-xs-12">
		        <ul class="mb-form-list-switches">
		          <li>
		            <label>
		              <input type="radio" name="order-summary-options">
		              <span class="mb-catalogue-filter-checkbox-wrapper"></span>
		              <span class="mb-catalogue-filter-title">
		                Der erste Händler.
		              </span>
		            </label>
		          </li>
		          <li>
		            <label>
		              <input type="radio" name="order-summary-options">
		              <span class="mb-catalogue-filter-checkbox-wrapper"></span>
		              <span class="mb-catalogue-filter-title">
		                Die zweite Händler.
		              </span>
		            </label>
		          </li>
		          <li>
		            <label>
		              <input type="radio" name="order-summary-options">
		              <span class="mb-catalogue-filter-checkbox-wrapper"></span>
		              <span class="mb-catalogue-filter-title">
		                Ein dritter Händler.
		              </span>
		            </label>
		          </li>
		        </ul>
		      </div>
		    </div>
		  </div>
		  <hr>
		  <h2>Wann möchten Sie beraten werden?</h2>
		  <div class="row">
		    <div class="col-xs-12">
		      <div class="row">
		        <div class="col-sm-6">
		          <div class="form-group">
		            <div class='input-group mb-date-wrapper' id='field-date-wrapper'>
		              <label for="field-1">Datum</label>
		              <div id="field-date"></div>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		        </div>
		        <div class="col-sm-3">
		          <div class="form-group">
		            <label for="field-5">Startzeit</label>
		            <select class="form-control" id="field-1">
		              <option value="">9 : 00 Uhr</option>
		              <option value="">10 : 00 Uhr</option>
		              <option value="">11 : 00 Uhr</option>
		            </select>
		            <label for="field-1" class="mb-select-arrow"></label>
		          </div>
		        </div>
		      </div>
		    </div>
		  </div>
		  <hr>

		  <h2>Wie können wir Sie erreichen?</h2>
		  <div class="row">
		    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
		      <div class="row">
		        <div class="col-xs-5">
		          <div class="form-group">
		            <label for="field-4">Anrede <sup>*</sup></label>
		            <select class="form-control" name="salutation" id="field-1">
		              <option value="">-</option>
		              <option value="">-</option>
		              <option value="">-</option>
		              <option value="">-</option>
		              <option value="">-</option>
		            </select>
		            <label for="field-1" class="mb-select-arrow"></label>
		            <span class="form-error-message">Enter value</span>
		          </div>
		        </div>
		        <div class="col-xs-7">
		          <div class="form-group">
		            <label for="field-5">Titel</label>
		            <select class="form-control" id="field-1">
		              <option value="">-</option>
		              <option value="">-</option>
		              <option value="">-</option>
		              <option value="">-</option>
		              <option value="">-</option>
		            </select>
		            <label for="field-1" class="mb-select-arrow"></label>
		          </div>
		        </div>
		      </div>
		    </div>
		  </div>
		  <div class="row">
		    <div class="col-xs-12">
		      <div class="row">
		        <div class="col-xs-6">
		          <div class="form-group">
		            <label for="field-9">Vorname <sup>*</sup></label>
		            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="firstName" id="field-9">
		            <span class="form-error-message">Enter value</span>
		          </div>
		        </div>
		        <div class="col-xs-6">
		          <div class="form-group">
		            <label for="field-5">Nachname <sup>*</sup></label>
		            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="lastName" id="field-5">
		            <span class="form-error-message">Enter value</span>
		          </div>
		        </div>
		      </div>
		    </div>
		  </div>
		  <div class="row">
		    <div class="col-xs-12">
		      <div class="row">
		        <div class="col-xs-6">
		          <div class="form-group">
		            <label for="field-9">E-Mail <sup>*</sup></label>
		            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="email" id="field-9">
		            <span class="form-error-message">Enter value</span>
		          </div>
		        </div>
		        <div class="col-xs-6">
		          <div class="form-group">
		            <label for="field-5">Telefon</label>
		            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="field-5" name="phone">
		          </div>
		        </div>
		      </div>
		    </div>
		    <label class="mb-form-sublabel"><sup>*</sup> Pflichtfelder</label>
		  </div>
		</div>
		<div class="modal-footer">
		  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mb-test-dive-form-navigation-next js-next">
		    Anfrage senden
		    <span class="mb-button-arrow-icon"></span>
		  </button>
		</div>
	</form>
	<div class="mb-test-drive_footer-dscr">
		<h3>Wo soll die Probefahrt beginnen?</h3>
		<h4>Für eine Probefahrt benötigen Sie einen gültigen EU-Führerschein. Der Kraftstoff wird nicht gestellt. 
		Vor Fahrantritt vereinbaren wir mit Ihneneinen Benutzungsvertrag mit einer Selbstbeteiligung von 1.000 € sowie eine gültige Datenschutzerklärung. Die Probefahrt findet ohne </h4>
	</div>
</div>
